ActEmergency Management Act
SubjectOrder No. 177 - (New Brunswick) Provincial Emergency Financial Assistance Order
PrecisPROVINCIAL EMERGENCY FINANCIAL ASSISTANCE ORDER NO. 177 which makes a declaration of federal concern and authorizes financial assistance to the province of NEW BRUNSWICK with respect to the SEVERE FLOODING, that affected a large part of the Province from April 15, 2014 to May 9, 2014.
